          "description": "Sets the minimum UNI token balance required to submit a governance proposal. When called via the GovernorBravoDelegator (proxy), the admin check resolves against the proxy's `admin` slot — currently the 48h Timelock — so changes go through standard governance. Bounded on-chain to MIN_PROPOSAL_THRESHOLD ≤ value ≤ MAX_PROPOSAL_THRESHOLD.",
