          "checked": true,
          "score": "critical",
          "description": "Nominates a new admin for the GovernorBravo proxy (two-step transfer; the nominee must then call `_acceptAdmin`). When invoked via the GovernorBravoDelegator, the admin check resolves against the proxy's `admin` slot — currently the 48h Timelock. Transferring this role would hand control of all GovernorBravo-level parameters (voting delay/period, proposal threshold, implementation upgrades) to the new admin, so any change is gated by the standard 48h governance delay.",
