          "checked": true,
          "score": "critical",
          "description": "Completes a two-step admin transfer by promoting the pending admin to admin on the GovernorBravo proxy. Caller must equal the proxy's `pendingAdmin` slot, which is currently the zero address — meaning no transfer is in flight. Becomes callable only after a successful `_setPendingAdmin`, which itself goes through the 48h Timelock.",
